# Collapse OpenSpec working artifacts in GitHub PR diffs.
# linguist-generated marks files as generated: hidden by default in PR
# diffs (expandable via "Load diff") and excluded from language stats.
# Files stay fully tracked in git — history and blame are unaffected.
# specs/ is intentionally NOT collapsed: spec deltas are the part
# reviewers must see.
openspec/changes/** linguist-generated=true
